title: God Has The Final Say
itunes:title: God Has The Final Say
description:
During times of discouragement, when it seems like you are at the mercy of your circumstances, know that God always has the final say. Whatever you are facing, you can live with confidence knowing that God has you in the palm of His hand. The battle belongs to Him!Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
